{
  "stem": "19690.3",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And so the health situation was tremendously bad.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "The food-- my Aunt Ruth was in the barracks and was barracks chief.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "She always managed to get involved in these kind of things.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "She would have to report every day for every meal how many people were in the barracks and then she would get food accordingly.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "In the morning, it was a watery coffee, that's it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "At noon, you got a soup which was made of rutabaga that you couldn't find and there were some chickpeas floating on top.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "The chickpeas were divided according to a list, one per person as far as the list went, and then the next day if there were four chickpeas on years on the soup that day, then the next four people on the list got a chickpea each.",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And then we got a ration of bread, which was about 250 grams.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And that was the bread for the day.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Then in the evening, we got another pot of soup.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And once in a while when the weather was really bad and the mud was very thick, sometimes the women carrying the soup between and two of them with probably two handles would stumble and some of the soup would spill.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And if they lost it, that's just too bad.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "There was just no soup that day.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "After a while, the decision was made that the children needed more food.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "They also made the decision that the children needed to be away from their parents.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We slept there.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then also they brought in tables and we started having school.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Like with everything that Jewish people do, educating the children is always the priority.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was here, too.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And some of the women who were or were not teachers would start teaching us French.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
